gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Pacers 127, Raptors 125
gameRecap.excerpt: The Pacers defeated the Raptors, 127-125. Pascal Siakam recorded 23 points, seven assists, and five rebounds in his return to Toronto, Tyrese Haliburton added 21 points and 12 assists for the Pacers in the victory. Scottie Barnes tallied 29 points, 12 rebounds, and eight assists for the Raptors in the losing effort. The Pacers improve to 31-25, while the Raptors fall to 19-36.
